{"tid":824421,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"為咗返工，今朝用咗二千幾蚊","createTime":"2018-09-17T05:24:53.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-23T04:24:58.000Z","uid":58998,"like":27,"dislike":28,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"253fa340c0dc017ae559090a59cae3fbdd0db94f","tid":824421,"uid":58998,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-17T05:24:53.000Z","msg":"是咁的，我係中環返clerk嘅，時薪就四十個半，算相當唔錯<br />\n咁我就住上水嘅<br />\n今朝係我唔好，無預到交通死哂.，咪照平時起身<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n咁朝早一上連登，先知今次大獲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n唔想遲到，惟有搭的士啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n點知收人頭六百出港島，唔理啦，返工最緊要，照搭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n返到公司，最後都遲咗三個字，俾老闆屌咗幾句，話今個月勤工獎無了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n好彩近來睇得多套乜乜攻略，下意識爆咗句: 係奴才唔啱，奴才無預好時間，令主子唔高興<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n主子聽到即刻笑返<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 話當無事<br />\n跟著之後又係做返啲routine嘢，送下件咁<br />\n我一睇地址，一封大埔，一封粉嶺，一封屯門....<br />\n老闆仲叫我速去速回<br />\n咁我見啲信唔係好急，都想問下可唔可以聽日送或者寄過去<br />\n但轉頭一諗，今朝先賴完嘢，都係出少句聲算<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n最後惟有搭的士啦，來回幾次，無咗二千幾蚊了<br />\n但老闆好好人，話破例俾我照巴士錢claim返<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n正常我無搭係無得claim的<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n咁就有驚無險一個朝早<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6bb8071a8a394eb86fd5f9e7c480c8cda789447c","tid":824421,"uid":68902,"like":4,"dislike":2,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-17T05:26:03.000Z","msg":"3.5/5"},{"pid":"a101f453af3652fe1226f53307423140872e0529","tid":824421,"uid":266,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-17T05:26:37.000Z","msg":"1/10"},{"pid":"e2a9dcb61b241f165adec1894f976cb3dc6558bc","tid":824421,"uid":28006,"like":5,"d